OL,3,CPrincess of Wales praised for telling
OL,4,Cher children of cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FExperts on child mental health have
OL,7,Fpraised the Princess of Wales in
OL,8,Ffacing the "unenviable task" of
OL,9,Ftelling her children about her cancer
OL,10,Fdiagnosis.
OL,12,FUniversity of Oxford associate
OL,13,Fprofessors Louise Dalton and Elizabeth
OL,14,FRapa stressed the importance of
OL,15,Fspeaking honestly to children and
OL,16,Fyoung people about serious illness.
