OL,3,CPrincess of Wales praised for telling
OL,4,Cher children of cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FThe academics, whose area of research
OL,7,Fspecifically focuses on talking to
OL,8,Fchildren about serious illness,
OL,9,Fpraised Kate for her "powerful and
OL,10,Fpersonal announcement" which
OL,11,Fhighlighted the challenging
OL,12,Fconversation facing millions of
OL,13,Fparents around the globe.
OL,15,FWilliam and Kate have focused on their
OL,16,Fchildren, taking the time to
OL,17,Fsensitively share the state of the
OL,18,Fprincess's health with Prince George,
OL,19,F10, Princess Charlotte, eight, and
OL,20,FPrince Louis, five.
