OL,3,CPrincess of Wales praised for telling
OL,4,Cher children of cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FIn a video released on Friday, Kate
OL,7,Fsaid: "It has taken us time to explain
OL,8,Feverything to George, Charlotte and
OL,9,FLouis in a way that is appropriate for
OL,10,Fthem, and to reassure them that I am
OL,11,Fgoing to be OK."
OL,13,FIt is understood the video was
OL,14,Freleased on the day William and Kate's
OL,15,Fthree children began their Easter
OL,16,Fschool holidays, to take advantage of
OL,17,Fthe break to shield them from coverage
OL,18,Fof their mother's health.
