OL,3,CPrincess of Wales praised for telling
OL,4,Cher children of cancer diagnosis
OL,6,F"Research shows that children want to
OL,7,Fknow about what is happening when an
OL,8,Fadult they love is ill and that
OL,9,Feffective communication with children
OL,10,Fabout illness is associated with
OL,11,Fbetter psychological functioning."
OL,13,FThe academics lead a programme of work
OL,14,Ffocused on the importance of
OL,15,Fcommunicating with children about a
OL,16,Floved one's serious illness such as
OL,17,Fcancer.
