OL,3,CPrincess of Wales praised for telling
OL,4,Cher children of cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FResearch suggests that when children
OL,7,Fare given an explanation of what is
OL,8,Fhappening in their family, it can lead
OL,9,Fto better family functioning and
OL,10,Fmental health outcomes.
OL,12,FProf Rapa said parents must also talk
OL,13,Fabout some of the emotional impact of
OL,14,Fthe news with their children.
