OL,3,CPrincess of Wales praised for telling
OL,4,Cher children of cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FShe added: "It's important to include
OL,7,Fchildren in conversations about
OL,8,Fillness in the family as soon as
OL,9,Fpossible so that they have time to
OL,10,Funderstand and make sense of the
OL,11,Fsituation and they are not left to
OL,12,Fworry alone.
OL,14,F"The powerful and personal
OL,15,Fannouncement by the Princess of Wales
OL,16,Ftoday highlights the unenviable task
OL,17,Ffacing millions."
